        "width": 420,
        "height": 216,
        "content": "### 3️⃣ Save to Supabase\nCreate a `leads` table before running, with columns:\n`name` (text), `phone` (text), `budget_range` (text), `property_type` (text), `location_preference` (text), `timeline` (text), `intent_score` (int4), `status` (text), `created_at` (timestamptz, default now())."
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
